p: \c[5]<outln>Persephone is insufferable. We tried to help her, bring her into our fold.</outln>
\c[5]<outln>It's a shame, really. Every person we fail to convert just makes our plan take longer to finish.</outln>
\c[5]<outln>And you see... I don't think we can exactly follow through with our mission of helping the world from down here.</outln>
\c[5]<outln>There's no easy way out, aside from using Darkrai's ability.</outln>
\c[5]<outln>...I have a feeling you already know where this is going.</outln>
\c[5]<outln>This world can't survive without the person in which it resides.</outln>
\c[5]<outln>It's a risky move, but it's the only one we see. Let's get this over with.</outln>
\c[5]<outln>It's a shame, too, \pn. I would have loved for you to join us.</outln>
\c[5]<outln>You're quite a battler. It's a shame you never chose to join us.</outln>
\c[5]<outln>We could have saved the region in days.</outln>
\c[5]<outln>We'll need to find another way out of here.</outln>
\c[5]<outln>I sensed another legendary Pokemon down here... perhaps they have a way to get out.</outln>
\c[5]<outln>Worse comes to worst, we could just... stay down here.\nThe people down here are corrupt. This would be the perfect place for us to help.</outln>.
\c[5]<outln>I'll need to give this some thought.</outln>
\c[5]Yeesh, you give a kid something to look after and their head grows three sizes.
